      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Samuel 14:39",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Samuel 19:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). It was unique to David to attach a further clause to this oath - a clause of thankfulness for some special mercy ",
        "children": []
